        "content": "<p>myunbin opened <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13850\">PR #13850</a> from <code>myunbin:add-rules-20260709-012308</code> to <code>bytecodealliance:main</code>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Add and modify simplification rules.</p>\n<h4><code>arithmetic.isle</code></h4>\n<ul>\n<li><code>-(~x) --&gt; x + 1</code></li>\n<li><code>~(-x) --&gt; x - 1</code></li>\n<li><code>-1 - x --&gt; ~x</code></li>\n</ul>\n<h4><code>bitops.isle</code></h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Modified rule <code>x ^ x --&gt; 0</code> to support vector types.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4><code>extends.isle</code></h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Keep only the narrowest type version.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4><code>icmp.isle</code></h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Add two rules: <code>~x == x --&gt; 0</code>, <code>~x != x --&gt; 1</code></li>\n<li>Modified rules for variants of <code>x == x --&gt; 1</code> to support vector types.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4><code>shifts.isle</code></h4>\n<ul>\n<li>All zeros/ones remain all zeros/ones for arithmetic right shifts or rotates.  <br>\nFor example, <code>0 &lt;&lt; x --&gt; 0</code> or <code>(-1) &gt;&gt;s x --&gt; (-1)</code>.<br>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>",
        "id": 609139741,
        "sender_full_name": "Wasmtime GitHub notifications bot",
        "timestamp": 1783574762
