    {
        "content": "<p>myunbin <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13850#issuecomment-4932559474\">commented</a> on <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13850\">PR #13850</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>@fitzgen As you suspected, <code>bxor</code> did not work for floats or vectors of floats. I updated<br>\nthe rule to support both cases and added tests.</p>\n</blockquote>",
