    {
        "content": "<p><span aria-label=\"speech balloon\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f4ac\" role=\"img\" title=\"speech balloon\">:speech_balloon:</span> myunbin created <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13850#discussion_r3556827664\">PR review comment</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Add an all-zero helper for float and vector types.</p>\n</blockquote>",
