    {
        "content": "<p><span aria-label=\"speech balloon\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f4ac\" role=\"img\" title=\"speech balloon\">:speech_balloon:</span> fitzgen created <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13850#discussion_r3615733479\">PR review comment</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>(sorry for the delayed response, just got back from vacation)</p>\n<p>Okay, I'll go ahead and enqueue this PR for merging, but regarding this:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>I believe adding <code>ir::Constant</code> helpers may be a better approach.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Would you be interested in investigating adding <code>ir::Constant</code> helpers and improving these rules in a follow up PR?</p>\n</blockquote>",
